title: Deadliest Catch Soundtrack (Extended)
description:
I took the Deadliest Catch Soundtrack and re edited the track listing and tags and added some new songs that were featured on the show plus the opening theme song which was not included on the cd.

Tracks on original CD: 18
Tracks on here: 21

The songs that were added have *** next to them.


1. Wanted Dead Or Alive (Opening Theme)***

2. A Deadly Catch

3. Paid

4. Roll Over

5. Western Theme/Lucky Lady

6. Urgent

7. The Storm

8. Irish Prayer

9. Between

10. Let It Soak

11. Res-Q

12. Leavin

13. Sea Theme

14. Crab King

15. Thunderrock

16. Rain

17. North Western/ Maverick Theme

18. Till The End

19. Pot Of Gold/Shanty

20. Oh Lord***

21. Gamblers Off The North Pacific Shore***
